[16443, 3, 1074040, 1122320, "It was narrated that Abu Umamah said:", "\"I said: 'O Messenger of Allah, tell me of an action (I should do).' He said: 'Take to fasting, for there is nothing equal to it.\"'", null, null, "Sahih (Darussalam)", null, "Book 22, Hadith 134", null, "Vol. 3, Book 22, Hadith 2225", "en"]
