[18264, 3, 1082625, 1140060, "It was narrated that 'Abdullah said:", "\"The Messenger of Allah [ﷺ] said: 'The first thing concerning which a person will be brought to account will be the Salah, and the first thing concerning which scores will be settled among the people, will be bloodshed.\"", null, null, "Sahih (Darussalam)", null, "Book 37, Hadith 26", null, "Vol. 5, Book 37, Hadith 3996", "en"]
