[19263, 3, 1087315, 1149520, "Makhramah narrated that his father said:", "\"I heard 'Uthman bin Abi AL-Walid, the freed slave of the Akhnasiyin, say: 'I heard 'Urwah bin Az-Zubair say;'Aishah used to narrated that the Prophet (ﷺ) said: \"The hand (of the htief) should notbe cut off for anything but a shield or its equivalent in value.\"'", null, null, "Sahih (Darussalam)", null, "Book 46, Hadith 68", null, "Vol. 5, Book 46, Hadith 4941", "en"]
[19264, 3, 1087320, 1149530, "'Uthman bin Abi Al-Walid said:", "\"I heard 'Urwah bin Az-Zubair say: \"Aishah used to narrate that he Prophet (ﷺ) of Allah said: The hand (of the thief) should not be cut off except for a shield or its equivalent in value. And he said that 'Urwah said: A shield is (worth) four Dirhams. And he (the narrator) said: I heard sulaiman bin Yasar say that he heard 'Amrah say: I heard 'Aishah narrate that she heard the Messenger of Allah say: The hand (of the thief) should not be cut off except for four Dinars or more.\"", null, null, "Sahih (Darussalam)", null, "Book 46, Hadith 69", null, "Vol. 5, Book 46, Hadith 4942", "en"]
