[19941, 3, 1090465, 1155550, "Abu Sa'eed Al-Khudri narrated that:", "The Prophet (ﷺ) [ﷺ] forbade mixing Al-Busr with dried dates, or raisins with dried dates, or raisins with Al-Busr, and he said: \"Whoever among you (wants to) drink them, let him drink each one on its own.\"", null, null, "Sahih (Darussalam)", null, "Book 51, Hadith 31", null, "Vol. 6, Book 51, Hadith 5572", "en"]
